```
  static Node parent(Node root,int token){
    Queue&lt;Node&gt; queue = new LinkedList&lt;&gt;();
    queue.add(root);
    while(!queue.isEmpty()){
      Node p = queue.poll();
      for(Node c: p.children){
        if(c.key == token) return p;
        queue.add(c);
      }
    }
    return null;
  }
```

